  schema:name "Predication" ;
  schema:description "The directed assignment of a value at a triple of subject, predicate, and object — the standard-mathematical articulation of what relationality calls relating, expressed through the predication cell, the predicate category and its four canonical generators, and the bilattice-valued fiber algebra." ;
